    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 3.399999694
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_04-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "おかえりなさいませ、ご主人様、お嬢様～！\nメイドの渚がお給仕させていただきますね～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.399999694,
      "endTime": 10.885487441199999,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cup-01.m4a",
          "delay": 11033.3335678
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 11.099999694
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_04-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "愛情たっぷりラブラブオムライス、お待たせしました！\n愛を注ぎますよ～美味しくなーれ、萌え萌えきゅ～ん！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.099999694,
      "endTime": 21.7799998084,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 19.5333332618
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 21.9666663606
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_04-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "あ、あれが噂に聞いてた萌え萌えキュン……\nさすがだわ、渚……あんなの私には絶対出来ない……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.9666663606,
      "endTime": 35.5053967912,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 13833.3335679
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 30.1999999285
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 35.6938777088
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_04-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "どうしよう、琴乃ちゃん！　想定以上の大人気で\nお客さんが溢れてる……メイドさんも全然足りないよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.6938777088,
      "endTime": 43.7390933155,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 43.8605461556
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_04-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "ええっ！？　そんなこと言ったって、もうメイドさんを\n出来る人は……よし、男子にも頼んでみましょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.8605461556,
      "endTime": 51.523741098100004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 48.9666665952
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 51.7122220157
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_04-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "ちがーう！　そこは実行委員が一肌脱がなきゃ！\n琴乃ちゃんの猫耳メイド服を買っておいて良かったよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.7122220157,
      "endTime": 60.218888008499995,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 60.4122217614
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_04-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "なんで用意してるのよ！　わ、私にはその格好は\n無理よ……！　ぜ、絶対似合わないから！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.4122217614,
      "endTime": 68.67773212959999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 68.8662130473
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_04-ngs005.m4a",
      "text": "わわわっ！！　ほらほら廊下にご主人様とお嬢様の\n行列が出来ちゃってるよ！　琴乃ちゃん早く～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.8662130473,
      "endTime": 76.8515873072,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_zawa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 0
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 77.0662130473
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_04-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "ううぅ……もうっ、着替えてくればいいんでしょ！\nはあ……猫耳メイド服なんて許可しなきゃ良かった……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.0662130473,
      "endTime": 88.1342174647,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 89.2726999082
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 90.7227014341
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_04-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "や、やっぱり……は、恥ずかしい～……\nこんな格好で接客なんて絶対に無理よ……無理！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.7227014341,
      "endTime": 99.5908424177,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 99.7793233352
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_04-ngs006.m4a",
      "text": "か、可愛い～……最高！　最高過ぎるよ琴乃ちゃん……\nもはや可愛いの暴力だよ……猫耳の破壊力たるや……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.7793233352,
      "endTime": 115.2044930892,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 115.4126566686
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "？？？",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "メイドさーん、こっちも注文お願いしま～す！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.4126566686,
      "endTime": 120.59084241769999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 120.7793233352
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_04-ngs007.m4a",
      "text": "はーい、すぐにお伺いしまーす！\nさ、琴乃ちゃん！　早くお給仕しに行こう！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.7793233352,
      "endTime": 128.1793232398,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_drag-01.m4a",
          "delay": 10254.009926600005
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 128.3793233352
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_04-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "ま、待って、まだ心の準備が……\nああ、手を引っ張らないで渚～～～……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.3793233352,
      "endTime": 135.9194542366,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 136.1079351542
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_04-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "お、お……お帰りなさいませ……お嬢様……\nめ、めめ……メイドの琴乃がお給仕します……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.1079351542,
      "endTime": 147.9685449716,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-camera-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5046.664632099975
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 125.39810760000591
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-camera-01.m4a",
          "delay": 13045.396073099993
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 142.6666665952
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 148.1570258893
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei Hayasaka",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_04-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "えへへへ～、琴乃ちゃんと渚ちゃんの\nメイドさん姿、可愛いね～！　ずっと見てたいな～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 148.1570258893,
      "endTime": 156.6970258512,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 149.7333312273
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 156.8570309756
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_04-ktn008.m4a",
      "text": "め、芽衣！？　やめて、写真撮影は禁止だってば！\n注文はど、ドーナツでいいわよね！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 156.8570309756,
      "endTime": 164.8972000238,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 165.0856809415
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei Hayasaka",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_04-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "ごめんね～、んー……ドーナツも食べたいけど～\n今日はラブラブオムライスがほしいな。琴乃ちゃんの！",
      "translations": {
